00:23:07,560 --> 00:23:15,510
...rather than losing our time to regret.

228
00:23:15,690 --> 00:23:18,910
Happiness is not something...

229
00:23:19,340 --> 00:23:23,740
...that someone does for me.

230
00:23:24,040 --> 00:23:32,310
It means that I have someone I can embrace.

231
00:23:41,990 --> 00:23:45,290
The Koushien tournament has ended, and summer is nearing its end.

232
00:23:45,290 --> 00:23:48,750
Yeah, but there's still one more event remaining.

233
00:23:48,750 --> 00:23:50,100
Oh, the fireworks display.

234
00:23:50,100 --> 00:23:53,470
That's right. So let's not be 
awkward with each other.

235
00:23:53,470 --> 00:23:54,490
What are you talking about ?

236
00:23:54,490 --> 00:23:57,620
I mean, about us 
spending the night together.

237
00:23:57,620 --> 00:23:59,480
I don't worry about that at all.

